{"tid":1614069,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【自己睇自己諗】【 Gear背後的勇氣】","createTime":"2019-10-02T16:37:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T23:40:18.000Z","uid":272569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3b927bfb972616cc7b7454bc6da026c43283c9","tid":1614069,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mZHJbN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mZHJbN&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7IpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=62df6a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mZHJbN</a><br />\n<br />\n#十一國殤【Gear背後的勇氣】<br />\n本台記者訪問正在上gear的年輕人花名阿偉，他表示上前線前已有心理準備並寫好遺書，更聲稱若某日「被自殺」發現屍體，願意透過器官捐贈貢獻他人。最後他更說：「為香港一定要贏呢場仗。」<br />\n[The Courage Behind Gears]<br />\n'I have been psychologically prepared &amp; written a will before I went to the frontline. If one day I was found &quot;suicide&quot;, I am willing to do the organ donation.' Finally, he said, 'We must win the battle for Hong Kong.'<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n#國殤日 #十一 #示威 #hongkongprotest #反送中 #香港警察 #hongkongpolice #watercannons #香港人 #遊行 #上街 #示威者 #勇武 #抗爭 #香港遊行 #催淚彈 #teargas #武器 #速龍 #防暴警察 #和理非 #城大 #cityu #protest #freehongkong #政府 #城大編委 #逆權運動 #社會運動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">每個人都有自己角色，<br />\n希望你地搵到自己應該要做咩！<br />\n<br />\n請用你嘅專長為自己地方出力，<br />\n希望你地唔好坐享其成，<br />\n食最後嘅血饅頭。<br />\n<br />\n佢地好需要支持支援，更希望有多啲勇武<br />\n10.1有手足中槍，佢係好彩先無死<br />\n但下次呢？到今日張贖罪卷已經好貴，貴到肉赤先夠<br />\n<br />\n唔夠膽衝可以幫手整器材，大大力課金買超級貴嘅贖罪卷，或去前面分水分嘢食，或接放學，借宿舍等等等等<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n希望將來煲底見到你地</span>"},{"pid":"d3baf0f3df23f3056cf497c659f1037a51789d99","tid":1614069,"uid":22131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8865c1ec83fe5a2d5c9e0a38b949e8fcd8f271e5","tid":1614069,"uid":283418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3baf0f3df23f3056cf497c659f1037a51789d99","tid":1614069